{"tid":28143,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[年經] 拍拖拍左幾耐先扑到","createTime":"2016-12-07T18:19:42.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-08T22:32:52.000Z","uid":17248,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"287a1bc54e7bb545d10aa8f9b05367fe365fd371","tid":28143,"uid":17248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T18:19:42.000Z","msg":"女朋友話係處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢成日都話唔會咁快就同我咩咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同佢一齊差唔多四個月<br />\n咩都玩過曬咁滯<br />\n就係唔肯扑<br />\n佢成日都話淨係可以插陰道上面個陰蒂<br />\n總之就點到即止<br />\n究竟幾時先可以破處呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d32b330de3746a8851c5296174aefa874d1df32","tid":28143,"uid":23156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T18:20:54.000Z","msg":"你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a18e51321951f5b1853e242fb4100ad350a9d8b5","tid":28143,"uid":16685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T18:21:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>女朋友話係處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢成日都話唔會咁快就同我咩咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同佢一齊差唔多四個月<br />\n咩都玩過曬咁滯<br />\n就係唔肯扑<br />\n佢成日都話淨係可以<span style=\"color: red;\">插陰道上面個陰蒂</span><br />\n總之就點到即止<br />\n究竟幾時先可以破處呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0bc68e8569fcaf72e0d7603f2042c9fdd9294b1","tid":28143,"uid":24358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T18:21:49.000Z","msg":"改個咁既名<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ea6a48fc6f9c2c6f0bc7a5f940dfce4c91ba596","tid":28143,"uid":24226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T18:22:45.000Z","m