ike":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T12:58:48.000Z","msg":"第一次拍拖雙方都係處果陣就拍左年幾先搞<br />\n之後果d 1 2個月"},{"pid":"f85c2342d47e6188e734d18d3a948911501ee043","tid":28143,"uid":57390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T13:01:28.000Z","msg":"最快嗰個八日，現任就兩星期內<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b827aaed74337bb7212f319c04722cc876e7a9b","tid":28143,"uid":23610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T13:03:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>女朋友話係處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢成日都話唔會咁快就同我咩咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同佢一齊差唔多四個月<br />\n咩都玩過曬咁滯<br />\n就係唔肯扑<br />\n佢成日都話淨係可以插陰道上面個陰蒂<br />\n總之就點到即止<br />\n究竟幾時先可以破處呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪又係雞"},{"pid":"7be1d4a40182677e809bfa6fd33e567335eb6bd5","tid":28143,"uid":54216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T13:03:29.000Z","msg":"四年半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你四個月都頂唔順，你都係遲早中出即飛嘅仆街嚟"},{"pid":"12310f87df7a85a805b0e1699c739edb8bcb1530","tid":28143,"uid":17248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T16:52:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>女朋友話係處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢成日都話唔會咁快就同我咩咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同佢一齊差唔多四個月<br />\n咩都玩過曬咁滯<br />\n就係唔肯扑<br />\n佢成日都話淨係可以插陰道上面個陰蒂<br />\n總之就點到即止<br />\n究竟幾時先可以破處呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪又係雞</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n見到你哩啲無女既毒撚淨係識話雞膠都廢是比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a287daa778e6d61992e1324ac051c2cdd9600b0","tid":28143,"uid":23752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T18:18:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>四年半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你四個月都頂唔順，你都係遲早中出即飛嘅仆街嚟</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中學開始拍？"},{"pid":"0c1028102648fc2b62825fcfd51add334f3cb81e","tid":28143,"uid":4105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T18:42:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>[(40-Af)^2+Lf^3]&times;10 &divide; [(Lm^2+Wm)&times;(Sf+1)^2] = N(第N日可啪) <br />\n<br />\nAf= 女方年齡(Age) 40歲以上女性本公式不適用 <br />\nLf= 女方外貌(Look) 10為滿分 <br />\nLm= 男方外貌(Look) 10為滿分 <br />\nWm= 男方資產(Worth) 每10萬港元為1個單位，不置上限，物業及汽車亦計算在內 <br />\nSf= 女方曾有性行為的男性數目(Sex Partner) <br />\n<br />\n例子1：中女&amp;amp;靚仔(有樓) <br />\n女 30歲 外貌7分 曾與2男有性行為 <br />\n男 外貌8分 資產300萬 <br />\n<br />\n[(40-30)^2+7^3]&times;10 &divide; [(8^2+30)&times;(2+1)^2] <br />\n=5.24日 <br />\n<br />\n例子2：毒向左走向右走&amp;amp;女神 <br />\n女 22歲 外貌9分 處女 <br />\n男 外貌3分 資產0 <br />\n<br />\n[(40-22)^2+9^3]&times;10 &divide; [(3^2+0)&times;(0+1)^2] <br />\n=1170日(不過捱得到去個日先算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ) <br />\n<br />\n利申：純理論，只作參考，實戰一定有誤差，過左理論日子都未啪到請先自我檢討。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"31fbde14599992676d69b6acf67fcca5e77596e8","tid":28143,"uid":2864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T18:42:31.000Z","msg":"一星期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87ddefef817a44f4898e521254ea66f6b8ad351a","tid":28143,"uid":61371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T18:43:34.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"9650c8fc49efe5953812fb04a50b515c958eff59","tid":28143,"uid":27793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T18:51:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>四年半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你四個月都頂唔順，你都係遲早中出即飛嘅仆街嚟</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nagger 樓豬咪撚溝處女 去ig search ptgf溝公廁啦<br />\n處女留俾巴打<br />\n無女唔會死 一樣可以diy解決<br />\n<br />\n回應番你：三年到分手都無破 因為互相尊重同愛惜"},{"pid":"47c4df4e239247a1834bed07a3e80d1008a140dd","tid":28143,"uid":54216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"